### 16. Algorithm Comparison: BFS vs DFS on complex route
### BFS - typically finds shortest path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/navigate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startNodeId": 2,
  "endNodeId": 25,
  "userProfile": "Regular",
  "algorithm": "BFS"
}

###

### DFS - may find longer path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/navigate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startNodeId": 2,
  "endNodeId": 25,
  "userProfile": "Regular",
  "algorithm": "DFS"
}

###

